title: Ep. #62 | Young K Takeover: Young K's Kpop Playlist
description:
Young K takes over hosting duties to discuss 'More & More' by TWICE, '내가 처음 만져본 강아지 (Love me)' by 원위 (ONEWE), and 'Colors' by Stella Jang. Stick around till the end as Young K reveals how he deals with burnout and what he loves to cook!


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
